text.tspan: Hope everyone had a good break. Thanks Jack for your progress update on the manufacturing end.
Before I continue I want to re-emphasize that this conversation should stay internal-eyes only.

more. I’ve plotted statistics for the JAAT interface angle over every run they did there. The plots are

I propose we change the mount angle to 10, or maybe even 15, degrees to the horizontal. That will

Those plots are fantastic, Tammy. Not exactly the best news, but I guess it’s better we find out now
